window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>Not even poison can keep Anthony down...</b></p> <p>Despite Selene’s attempt at manipulating him, Anthony is back on his feet—thanks to Marianne. His new vampire roommate has been proving talented at not just housework, but also at helping him with other matters. It’s only a matter of time before he takes their relationship to the next level.</p> <p>The peace conference is coming up soon, and many dignitaries are arriving on Academy Island to re-sign the Demonic Covenant, the peace treatise that allows humans and demons to co-exist.</p> <p>But there are people working in the background who do not want peace. They will stop at nothing to destroy the peace many others have worked so hard for...even if it costs tens of millions of lives.</p> <p><b>Warning: contains mature content.</b></p>"; 
